{"tid":618704,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人浸過河口湖既開運之湯??","createTime":"2018-04-06T04:24:21.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-10T02:44:54.000Z","uid":59844,"like":0,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"33ce455a54bd34582c4dc53ceff644519e6cf9cf","tid":618704,"uid":59844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-06T04:24:21.000Z","msg":"我16年暑假去過一次,浸完之後有拖拍兼股市大賺,17年仲升職加薪,之後覺得好似有料到。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n所以岩岩17年年尾去東京果陣去ENCORE,本來新工作唔太順利,工作壓力大,老闆又變態<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ,浸完番來,果個變態老闆又調走,仲要無喇喇公司開2個位分擔工作,宜家工作算係輕輕鬆鬆鄧子峰。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我最近有朋友去東京玩,聽我講完呢個經歷之後,佢又去左浸,朋友一浸完果日就收到WHATAPPS MSG 叫佢去interview見老師,朋友本身係助教,做左成10年都未試過收到INTERVIEW見老師。<br />\n<br />\n有冇人有浸過呢個湯? 浸完之後有冇用?? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bfc971cd7f194b0b04e65687963f801b66c8cb9b","tid":618704,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-06T04:26:30.000Z","msg":"瑞士山區肺"},{"pid":"7d4238fc73ffec0dcdbab475b6427b98ea4d0688","tid":618704,"uid":59844,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"bfc971cd7f194b0b04e65687963f801b66c8cb9b","tid":618704,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-06T04:26:30.000Z","msg":"瑞士山區肺"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-09T23:59:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b5006cbbfdf7441c381536177040976c6f69b1d","tid":618704,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-10T00:09:39.000Z","msg":"我浸完之後聰明左<br />\n次次默書得一百分添呀"},{"pid":"a19454f9ba0152f402cc96c469753a0aba6b988c","tid":618704,"uid":59844,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"4b5006cbbfdf7441c381536177040976c6f69b1d","tid":618704,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-10T00:09:39.000Z","msg":"我浸完之後聰明左<br />\n次次默書得一